Unlock Your Child’s Summer Potential!
ESTEAM Summer Camp (Environment, Science, Technology, Engineering, Art & Math) is back from June 16 – August 8, 2025 for youth ages 6–11!

Monday–Friday | 7AM – 6PM
Kids will dive into outdoor fun, robotics, coding, art, games, and more through exciting weekly themes like Galactic Explorers, CSI Discovery, Dream Builders, and more!

FREE snacks included + tons of hands-on learning!
Register now – spaces fill up fast!

Scan the QR code or visit your local LA County park for details.
